482
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:41,200
I mean the statistics I’ve not seen but will go down.

483
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:45,960
It’s a left side attack and the more you try to go to left side

484
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,285
there will be more attacks.

485
00:36:47,366 --> 00:36:50,366
Right side attacks are also lots of these wars.

486
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:53,560
All these wars and all these things take place

487
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:55,840
because we are invaded from the right side.

488
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,640
All these aggressive people

489
00:36:57,880 --> 00:37:01,240
like Hitler and all that are aggressing us.

490
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:09,880
How much it is necessary for you to rise above your lower self.

491
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:11,720
One should understand that

492
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:15,520
and not to indulge into nonsense that you are doing.

493
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,880
You have to really work hard for that.

494
00:37:17,999 --> 00:37:23,640
Even if you have to get up early in the morning, you have to get up and do it.

495
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:30,640
You should understand your responsibilities, that’s the main point.

496
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:34,400
People are now busy only doing jobs, working here, how much money

497
00:37:34,481 --> 00:37:37,393
you get, how much do you go, when do you go to job and all that.

498
00:37:37,474 --> 00:37:39,194
That’s not important for us.

499
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:43,359
Now that doesn’t mean you give up your jobs and be a liability on the ashram,

500
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:46,600
it doesn’t mean that! It means you do your jobs, have money,

501
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:50,040
money is needed for the work. I need money, you know that how much

502
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:51,999
money we need for all this work.

503
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:54,999
You have taken such a big project of going to Europe

504
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,320
having this little money.

505
00:37:57,560 --> 00:38:00,999
It’s not possible. But we are doing it somehow.

506
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:04,200
So, we need money, you have to earn, you have to give;

507
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:06,400
you have to give money. Here people are,

508
00:38:06,481 --> 00:38:08,599
they are not even willing to give ten pounds.

509
00:38:08,680 --> 00:38:14,640
Such people. With them where am I going to do Sahaj Yoga?

510
00:38:16,640 --> 00:38:20,040
We are so attached to money in a subtler way.

511
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:25,280
We do not understand we have to give money and we have to do it up.

512
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:27,999
Not only money, money’s not the only solution;

513
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:30,160
we have to be ourselves channels.

514
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,200
But then some people have money,

515
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:37,440
then they are exploited in a wrong way and the money’s all wasted.

516
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:40,960
This is precious money, this is auspicious money,

517
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:45,480
this money goes into the right hands into right places.

518
00:38:45,720 --> 00:38:49,640
Problems are created because of that.

519
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:54,520
Now this money I do not need, you know that very well.

520
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:57,359
But for your own betterment you have to give money.

521
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:58,960
Ask Gavin he’ll tell you.

522
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:04,120
He’s a very generous man and he, he found it very good.

523
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:08,720
It’s not that I need a single pai from you.

524
00:39:08,833 --> 00:39:11,759
On the contrary I am willing to spend My own money on things,

525
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:13,520
you know that definitely.

526
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:18,520
But, you must understand this work has to be done, so you need money.

527
00:39:18,721 --> 00:39:20,960
I need not tell you that you have to pay money.

528
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:23,307
I have never said this to Indians, I have never told them.

529
00:39:23,388 --> 00:39:25,440
They have never given Me a problem you’ll be amazed.

530
00:39:25,521 --> 00:39:27,399
How they solve their problems God alone knows.

531
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:28,839
They are not the people of money.

532
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:31,560
There’s never a quarrel about money. Nobody talks about money,

533
00:39:31,641 --> 00:39:33,918
nobody tells Me anything, nothing of the kind.

534
00:39:33,999 --> 00:39:37,480
Nobody oppresses anyone or mishandles anyone

535
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:40,827
or controls anyone, everybody does so well.

536
00:39:41,002 --> 00:39:44,119
Money is not with one person. Say about two, three people handle it.

537
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:47,880
Everybody knows how much money they are taking.

538
00:39:48,240 --> 00:39:50,000
This one part is important.

539
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:55,280
For solving this problem you give Me rice.

540
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,520
It’s called as “Oti bharne,”

541
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:03,760
that you give Me rice I beg of you, actually. You put it in My sari.

542
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:09,280
Rice, you give Me five times, I give you seven times back.

543
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,760
That’s the symbol. You know how symbols work out.

544
00:40:12,999 --> 00:40:16,760
Even when you say, “Mother are you the Holy Ghost?” it works out,

545
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:20,000
it gives you realization.

546
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:27,800
If there is somebody so alert and sensitive sitting before you,

547
00:40:27,999 --> 00:40:32,720
you must know how to do the symbols, how to do them properly,

548
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:38,960
with full maturity, understanding, in the proper way.

549
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:42,760
You are very anxious to do the puja, but do you understand,

550
00:40:42,999 --> 00:40:47,000
before the puja always there’s a quarrel going on.

551
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:50,760
Somebody who is a very possessed person will come, to begin with,

552
00:40:50,999 --> 00:40:54,200
and everybody will start fighting. Imagine!

553
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:58,760
You must take your bath, “What are you doing?”

554
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:04,320
In the morning don’t talk to anyone. Be in hush condition.

555
00:41:04,560 --> 00:41:09,320
You are in for opening out to the great power,

556
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:14,000
which is going to solve the problem of the world.

557
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:20,400
So you cleanse yourself, you wash yourself; you cleanse yourself,

558
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:25,000
so that you get your chakras evolved.

559
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:30,640
People talked against it because they became only ritualistic,

560
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:33,440
mechanical; matter became very important.

561
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:35,999
Then only doing these things became important.

562
00:41:36,120 --> 00:41:41,160
But not now, you people are different. You are realized souls.

563
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:46,439
That doesn’t mean that you should take to sanyasa or anything.

564
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:49,600
You should, I’ve told you, you should live like normal people,

565
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,920
but a very dignified people.

566
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:58,200
Nothing of indignity, childishness, superfluousness or joker-like,

567
00:41:58,440 --> 00:42:02,200
clown-like, outstandingly funny, all these dresses should not be worn.

568
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:05,799
You should be properly dressed in a way that you have a presence.

569
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:08,880
I mean this is to a children I am telling you.

570
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:12,520
You must have a presence of grown up Sahaja Yogis, You are all saints.

571
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,999
You know such a lot even many saints do not know.

572
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:17,760
You can go and ask so many of them.

573
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:20,999
There’s one thing they know that I am that.

574
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:27,999
That’s one thing you do not know. They know that.

575
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:30,560
This is a big difference.

576
00:42:30,641 --> 00:42:33,399
Because I am easily available to you, you do not understand.

577
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:37,240
For them I am great. As I told you yesterday that how these saints

578
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:41,680
have recognized and they have sent people to help Me.

579
00:42:42,999 --> 00:42:47,000
In saintliness only, your recognition of Me is poor.

580
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:50,520
Because if it was not, you would not be shouting in My presence,

581
00:42:50,688 --> 00:42:52,999
quarrelling in My presence. You give Me headaches,

582
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:56,000
you tell Me things, which you should not tell Me.

583
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:59,520
“He knocked at my door,” somebody tells Me.

584
00:42:59,633 --> 00:43:02,239
He says “he came there, he did this,” another tells Me.

585
00:43:02,320 --> 00:43:07,320
You should not talk like this to Me.

586
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:14,360
You are materially again bound by talking.

587
00:43:14,600 --> 00:43:18,080
From where does the talk come from? Vishuddhi.

588
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:22,120
Talk comes from Vishuddhi, but it starts from, the whole vani,

589
00:43:22,360 --> 00:43:30,920
the whole sound starts from much below. So, to raise it higher

590
00:43:31,080 --> 00:43:36,480
there are stages of this sound coming in.

591
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:39,960
And when it becomes madhyama, is in the heart,

592
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:42,840
in the heart region where it just throbs,

593
00:43:42,999 --> 00:43:47,960
you do not feel the throbbing. Then it comes here.

594
00:43:48,520 --> 00:43:52,120
Here it becomes vaikhari.

595
00:43:53,520 --> 00:44:01,120
Then it becomes pashyanti means it sees, it just sees.

596
00:44:01,800 --> 00:44:06,960
Then it becomes Para, where it becomes just silent

597
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:11,680
in the aweness of the presence.

598
00:44:14,760 --> 00:44:20,999
We have to develop those things. But we do not understand

599
00:44:21,120 --> 00:44:25,000
that all these things are our attributes,

600
00:44:25,280 --> 00:44:28,000
which we have to enlighten and rise.

601
00:44:28,640 --> 00:44:34,560
And make every part, every petal of our being beautiful.

602
00:44:37,360 --> 00:44:41,720
If you start understanding these small, small things,

603
00:44:41,999 --> 00:44:47,960
which are very important because I am talking of very big things.

604
00:44:48,040 --> 00:44:53,840
But even a small thing can close your eyes completely.

605
00:44:55,000 --> 00:45:00,000
It’s a very big vision I have, very big vision.

606
00:45:00,800 --> 00:45:03,040
And that vision can be done through you people.

607
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:05,600
You do not think that you are ordinary.

608
00:45:05,840 --> 00:45:08,600
Otherwise I would never have chosen you.

609
00:45:09,200 --> 00:45:11,960
But you have no recognition of yourself also,

610
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:14,000
as you have no recognition of Me.

611
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:19,960
You have to recognize yourselves and respect yourself.

612
00:45:23,600 --> 00:45:27,680
Do not respect material things, respect yourself first of all

613
00:45:27,920 --> 00:45:29,560
and the matter within you.

614
00:45:29,800 --> 00:45:34,120
If you move that way I think you’ll understand better what I am saying.

615
00:45:36,920 --> 00:45:42,040
The body of a human being is a temple of God.

616
00:45:42,440 --> 00:45:48,760
But this temple has to be enlightened and has to be auspicious.

617
00:45:49,960 --> 00:45:54,400
You have to clear and clean your being completely

618
00:45:54,640 --> 00:45:58,760
so it’s a beautiful temple for God to reside there.

619
00:45:59,999 --> 00:46:01,960
But we deceive ourselves, you see?

620
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:05,600
When I am talking, you listen to Me

621
00:46:05,999 --> 00:46:09,160
and you think that “Oh, Mother talked very sweetly, beautifully,”

622
00:46:09,440 --> 00:46:12,480
finished. But nothing goes inside.

623
00:46:12,760 --> 00:46:15,920
Why? Because of lethargy.

624
00:46:16,280 --> 00:46:18,280
Lethargy is a thing, which is a barrier.

625
00:46:18,680 --> 00:46:21,640
It doesn’t allow Me to go inside you.

626
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:23,040
It’s a barrier.

627
00:46:23,208 --> 00:46:25,960
It’s very sweet thing, which smiles, just you see thinking,

628
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:29,680
“Oh, Mother is saying something nice, it’s very great,”

629
00:46:29,923 --> 00:46:31,719
it gives you happiness and all that,

630
00:46:31,800 --> 00:46:36,080
but it doesn’t go inside, you do not imbibe.

631
00:46:36,520 --> 00:46:39,120
And that’s why, try to put your attention to yourself

632
00:46:39,360 --> 00:46:41,400
and feel your dignity and honor.

633
00:46:41,960 --> 00:46:46,440
Feel your presence that you have to have a presence

634
00:46:46,840 --> 00:46:49,608
and when I tell to some people, they’ll say, “I know,

635
00:46:49,689 --> 00:46:51,919
Mother, I know I do that.”

636
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:54,960
Then why do you do it? That means you are possessed.

637
00:46:55,120 --> 00:46:58,120
You are a possessed person that you know this is wrong,

638
00:46:58,400 --> 00:47:01,800
still you are doing it. Then you are a possessed person.

639
00:47:01,999 --> 00:47:04,000
Then is better you beat yourself with shoes.

640
00:47:04,320 --> 00:47:07,960
But that stage should go now, I don’t like you to beat yourself with shoes,

641
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:11,000
I mean are you that, that level?

642
00:47:11,999 --> 00:47:16,040
But the level is such still.

643
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:21,560
And your presence is the one that should give Prasannata,

644
00:47:21,999 --> 00:47:24,240
is the cheerfulness to others.

645
00:47:24,920 --> 00:47:29,400
Others should feel cheerful in your company.

646
00:47:30,480 --> 00:47:35,880
A presence is something, which you can understand.

647
00:47:36,999 --> 00:47:39,999
A presence has prudence.

648
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:45,520
It understand how to behave in a particular thing.

649
00:47:47,440 --> 00:47:51,520
It is not imprudent like it won’t rush to a thing.

650
00:47:51,920 --> 00:47:54,520
It won’t jump on to a thing. If somebody is talking

651
00:47:54,920 --> 00:47:59,000
you just do not become absolutely dominating on that.

652
00:47:59,640 --> 00:48:03,000
When you talk, you do not talk in a way that is dramatic

653
00:48:03,320 --> 00:48:06,440
or sort of theatrical; or neither you talk in a way

654
00:48:06,680 --> 00:48:08,720
that is lunatic-like or something like that.

655
00:48:08,960 --> 00:48:11,480
Presence has its own balance in the center

656
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:14,520
and that presence must be maintained.

657
00:48:14,920 --> 00:48:17,999
Presence is very important and just see yourself:

658
00:48:18,160 --> 00:48:22,800
are you having a presence?

659
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:26,200
Some people are very good Sahaj Yogis, but they have no “go,”

660
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:31,200
they have no dash, at all. They receive things, they see things,

661
00:48:31,999 --> 00:48:37,880
they should have a dash. They have to tell people,

662
00:48:38,400 --> 00:48:42,560
but in a way that is congenial, that is sweet, that is beautiful,

663
00:48:42,800 --> 00:48:48,720
that works is the point. If it does not work, what’s the use?

664
00:48:49,160 --> 00:48:52,160
Now again I am going for seventeen days.

665
00:48:52,440 --> 00:48:54,760
Really seventeen days I’ll be out.

666
00:48:54,999 --> 00:49:01,000
I miss you all very much and I feel concerned so much,

667
00:49:01,840 --> 00:49:05,880
because you have to still grow quite a lot.

668
00:49:06,999 --> 00:49:14,999
I feel that among you there is no understanding of collectivity.

669
00:49:16,720 --> 00:49:20,960
A very irritable people; you get irritable with each other,

670
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:27,280
how can you? You are all saints. You must respect each other;

671
00:49:27,640 --> 00:49:29,000
you must love each other,

672
00:49:29,280 --> 00:49:33,800
talk sweetly to each other. You are all saints!

673
00:49:34,120 --> 00:49:38,200
A saint meets another saint, how does he meet?

674
00:49:38,440 --> 00:49:43,800
Have you seen anytime, a real saint meeting another real saint?

675
00:49:45,560 --> 00:49:52,400
You should see. You do not look like that. The first proof is this.

676
00:49:52,640 --> 00:49:57,999
Are you really saints or not. He has gone to India, how they met you?

677
00:49:59,362 --> 00:50:02,560
Yogi: Take really hold of me. Shri Mataji: See? Yogi: I couldn’t believe him …

678
00:50:02,672 --> 00:50:04,439
Shri Mataji: How they meet each other!

679
00:50:04,520 --> 00:50:07,360
They’ll hug each other and they enjoy each other’s company.

680
00:50:07,600 --> 00:50:13,040
They laugh at jokes and understand it is such a congenial thing.

681
00:50:13,440 --> 00:50:15,960
Nobody thinks,  “I am right.” Nobody thinks like that.

682
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:18,815
Once you start thinking, “I am right and that person is wrong.”

683
00:50:18,896 --> 00:50:22,440
“I am doing all right, he’s wrong,” finished.

684
00:50:22,880 --> 00:50:26,080
They enjoy themselves so much just like one wave it moves, you see?

685
00:50:26,680 --> 00:50:31,999
They are all the time laughing, enjoying you know, loudly.

686
00:50:32,480 --> 00:50:37,960
They help each other such a lot. It’s absolutely worth seeing that.

687
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:42,240
While we had only five or six people to begin with,

688
00:50:42,480 --> 00:50:48,320
in Nilambar, from London. One better than the other.

689
00:50:48,999 --> 00:50:53,000
They are all fighting, quarrelling and they used to come up to beating.

690
00:50:53,240 --> 00:50:57,640
Can you believe it? This was happening.

691
00:50:57,999 --> 00:51:01,960
So shameful I tell you and everybody was coming and telling,

692
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:08,960
“What sort of Sahaj Yogis you have got, Mother? Are they Sahaj Yogis, really?”

693
00:51:09,480 --> 00:51:11,560
Arguing and doing this and doing that.

694
00:51:11,800 --> 00:51:16,160
All sorts of things were on and they would not inform Me the whole of it,

695
00:51:16,400 --> 00:51:25,160
but part of it would come to Me. I was so ashamed. Ask Malcolm.

696
00:51:26,200 --> 00:51:31,280
They used to, I mean they would break each other’s heads there.

697
00:51:31,520 --> 00:51:36,280
This was the condition. Can you believe it?

698
00:51:37,999 --> 00:51:42,720
While you would never find any Sahaj Yogis doing that, never, in India.

699
00:51:42,999 --> 00:51:46,760
I have not seen anyone. Anybody who tries to be funny goes out,

700
00:51:47,000 --> 00:51:48,999
immediately out of circulation.

701
00:51:49,120 --> 00:51:52,880
There’s no group-forming, nobody fights with anybody, nothing.

702
00:51:52,999 --> 00:51:56,480
And everybody was surprised how strange these people were,

703
00:51:56,720 --> 00:52:05,000
one better than the other. They were very irritable, hot-tempered, fighting and all that.

704
00:52:05,280 --> 00:52:10,040
They were so surprised that how can there be.

705
00:52:11,280 --> 00:52:13,760
Give you an example here of Chhaya, see.

706
00:52:13,999 --> 00:52:16,760
Despite, she’s quite shocked;

707
00:52:17,160 --> 00:52:20,800
but she doesn’t know how to really beat things, meet.

708
00:52:20,999 --> 00:52:23,480
People are so criticizing, so this thing,

709
00:52:23,720 --> 00:52:30,480
but she’s trying to keep the balance. She’ll be always at the back.

710
00:52:31,000 --> 00:52:34,960
She’s never in the forward, when it comes to work she’ll be the first to do it.

711
00:52:35,000 --> 00:52:44,960
She takes up responsibilities. This is what happened last time.

712
00:52:45,560 --> 00:52:47,200
It’s not only lethargy,

713
00:52:47,440 --> 00:52:51,080
it is worse than that. In lethargy, you see it is a devil’s mind,

714
00:52:51,320 --> 00:52:55,040
and when you come out of lethargy you just come to blows.

715
00:52:55,560 --> 00:52:59,680
But as it is in India, I’ve not seen people coming to blows, I really tell you.

716
00:52:59,920 --> 00:53:02,680
Very seldom you’ll find people coming to blows.

717
00:53:03,000 --> 00:53:08,960
I mean, people never even talk loudly or in a temper, never.

718
00:53:09,200 --> 00:53:14,560
Now normally people are very quiet type. Then Sahaj Yogis,

719
00:53:14,800 --> 00:53:17,000
Oh! You should see how they enjoy.

