Only when it is a special puja or they tie up –

918
01:05:48,320 --> 01:05:50,520
in Maharashtra, there I agree.

919
01:05:50,760 --> 01:05:53,800
But I never make a bun and put a thing. It’s all right,

920
01:05:53,999 --> 01:05:55,480
if he doesn’t like it why do it?

921
01:05:55,720 --> 01:06:01,440
Unnecessary to increase all the clashes and the problem.

922
01:06:01,680 --> 01:06:04,840
Don’t do anything that people do not like you to do.

923
01:06:04,999 --> 01:06:08,720
Try to avoid, it creates problems.

924
01:06:08,817 --> 01:06:10,719
Try to do something that pleases others.

925
01:06:10,800 --> 01:06:14,240
Let us see if you have devised this method how to please.

926
01:06:14,480 --> 01:06:16,999
If you please others, your deities will be very happy,

927
01:06:17,200 --> 01:06:18,999
because they are all one,

928
01:06:19,040 --> 01:06:23,520
within you, within her, within her, they are all one.

929
01:06:23,760 --> 01:06:26,960
And they feel happy, because they’re all related to each other,

930
01:06:27,000 --> 01:06:30,560
and they feel unhappy when you try to be unkind to each other,

931
01:06:30,800 --> 01:06:34,200
because they are one.

932
01:06:34,999 --> 01:06:38,680
If this is worked out, properly, understandingly,

933
01:06:38,920 --> 01:06:40,960
all of you are going to be great saints.

934
01:06:41,000 --> 01:06:43,800
I see your image in future also.

935
01:06:43,999 --> 01:06:46,880
Of some of you are going to be very, very great

936
01:06:46,999 --> 01:06:48,999
and some of you are going to take it up.

937
01:06:49,160 --> 01:06:52,400
It’s a, it’s a project launched.

938
01:06:52,680 --> 01:06:54,560
Launch a project against yourself,

939
01:06:54,800 --> 01:06:57,600
towards yourself, building up yourself.

940
01:06:57,880 --> 01:07:01,160
How sweet you are going to be others, let’s have it.

941
01:07:01,600 --> 01:07:03,760
Talk to others. Some people just don’t talk,

942
01:07:03,848 --> 01:07:05,999
I have seen they are all the time …[SILENCE];

943
01:07:06,240 --> 01:07:08,280
they will have very bad Vishuddhi.

944
01:07:08,520 --> 01:07:12,000
You must talk; you must be nice you must be open-hearted.

945
01:07:12,240 --> 01:07:14,239
This Yugoslav girl is very open–hearted,

946
01:07:14,320 --> 01:07:17,600
I like her for that reason. She has a big heart.

947
01:07:17,840 --> 01:07:19,880
Talk with a big heart, open!

948
01:07:20,000 --> 01:07:26,960
No secretiveness and this cold, what is it called, English manner?

949
01:07:27,000 --> 01:07:31,960
Yogini: Aloof? Shri Mataji: Aloof?

