1222
01:24:58,000 --> 01:25:04,960
How you treat them? What racialism you have here compared to what we have in India,

1223
01:25:05,000 --> 01:25:07,960
we have no racialism. They treated you with such great respect.

1224
01:25:08,000 --> 01:25:11,960
