1225
01:25:12,000 --> 01:25:19,960
But if you go to Africa they will teach you. Africans, West Indies – they are on top of you.

1226
01:25:20,000 --> 01:25:24,960
What I’m saying, to break the vicious circle try to understand the problem of every country.

