1274
01:29:07,000 --> 01:29:10,960
Now this is the worst thing that can happen to anyone; that we have realized very soon,

1275
01:29:11,000 --> 01:29:13,960
I hope they have withdrawn it. So they what they did –

1276
01:29:14,000 --> 01:29:15,960
Indians as it is they are very cunning and clever –

1277
01:29:16,000 --> 01:29:19,960
so what they did they would go and write their names as the people who are doles,

1278
01:29:20,000 --> 01:29:23,960
